      "content" : "VMware PowerBlock | August 2022 --- The August PowerBlock is absolutely going to be a well attended event. We are gong to have an all-star lineup, of highly qualified automation engineers, including Ariel Sanchez, Tom Gillaspy, Chris McClanahan, Dale Hassinger and our powerblock discussing a variety of topics. Here is the general outline for the conversation: How do you get started with automation? What does success look like? What are some of the common mistakes \/ misperceptions when getting started with automation? What are some examples of customer success using vRealize Automation? --- [youtube:Mswok2Q4E8w] --- <div> <br> <\/div> Why Automate? How to get started? What does success look like? What are some common mistakes \/ misperception's Examples of customer success ---",
